{"word":"G3729 - ὁρμάω - hormáō - hor-mah'-o - Run","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁρμάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hormáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hor-mah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Run</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஓடு, பாய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to set in rapid motion, stir up, incite, urge on"},{"paragraph":"2. intransitive, to start forward impetuously, to rush"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3730 - ὁρμή - hormḗ - hor-may'/3730\">G3730</a>; to <i>start</i>, <i>spur</i> or <i>urge</i> on, that is, (reflexively) to <i>dash</i> or <i>plunge:</i> - run (violently), rush.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3729/3729\">G3729</a>, <a href=\"#/G3730/3730\">G3730</a>, <a href=\"#/G3731/3731\">G3731</a>, <a href=\"#/G874/874\">G874</a>"}]}